Title: Probie
Plot: While on duty, McGee kills a man who is later discovered to be an undercover police officer. When Jenny decides to approve the investigation on McGee, the NCIS team is forced to prove that McGee is not guilty, pushing Gibbs' relationship with Jen to the limit.  Meanwhile, Tony is troubled by his past.
ParentalRatingReason: R13 Violence and content that may disturb
GuestStars: Christopher Allport, William Gregory Lee, Brian Dietzen
